USB Connectors
--------------

There are 4 x dual **USB 2.0 HOST connectors** onboard, as shown in the figure below.

.. Figure:: /Media/ARM/A72/PPC_Others/USB.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center

  *USB 2.0 HOST Connectors*

There is also 1 x **USB 3.0 HOST connector** and 1 x **USB Type-C connector**, as shown below.

.. Figure:: /Media/ARM/A72/PPC_Others/USB3.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center

  *USB 3.0 HOST Connector*

.. Figure:: /Media/ARM/A72/PPC_Others/USB-C.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center

  *USB Type-C Connector*
